high_descs: Pick up the pan from the back left.
Turn around and take the pan to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the pan inside for a little bit and then take it out.
Turn right to the cupboard next to the fridge.
Put the pan away in the cupboard.
anns.task_desc: Chill the pan and put it away in the cupboard.

high_descs: Move to the stove to the right of the sink
Pick up a pan from the stove
Move to the fridge behind you
Chill the pan in the fridge for a moment then pick it up and close the door
Move to the right of the fridge to the cabinet
Put the pan in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan in the bottom cabinet closest to the fridge.

high_descs: Turn completely around to face the stove.
Pick up the pan from the left back burner.
Turn around completely and walk over to the fridge.
Place the pan in the fridge, close the door, then open it the door and retrieve the pan.
Open the white cabinet door that is under the counter to the right of the fridge.
Place the pan inside the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled off pan into a cabinet.
